  <brief_title>Phase Ib Study of PDR001 in Combination With Regorafenib in Adult Patients With Previously Treated Metastatic Colorectal Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase Ib Study of PDR001 in Combination With Regorafenib in Adult Patients With Previously Treated Metastatic Microsatellite Stable (MSS) Colorectal Cancer</official_title>
